    "title": "Mobile Money & Digital Payments",
    "subtitle": "Female mobile ownership and UPI transaction volume by state",
    "source": "NFHS-5 2019–21, IIPS/MoHFW (mobile ownership); RBI Payment System Data (UPI)",
